<div id="outline-container-org9b79f88" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org9b79f88">To link to work in tasks:</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org9b79f88">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>In Tasks: Create the link (<code>org-store-link</code>)  Ive bound to <code>C-c s</code></li>
<li>Then in the daily <code>C-c C-l</code></li>
</ul>
<p>
[[[BROKEN LINK: No match for fuzzy expression: *Projectile] and Magit][
</p>
</div>
