<div id="outline-container-orgf4fee9b" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgf4fee9b">Link to Email</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgf4fee9b">
<p>
<code>- org-store-line [C-c s]</code> on the mail in view mail
</p>
<ul class="org-ul">
<li><code>C-c C-l</code> where you want to put the link</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgc4dc7f6" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgc4dc7f6">Can link to files on the file system! <a href="org_roam_tips-20250503175045.html#ID-7391CD68-2E3C-4FB0-B1E2-5BDAC7CCF2B9">Org-Roam-Tips</a></h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgc4dc7f6">
<p>
<code>C-c C-l</code> then do <code>file:</code> RET and then navigate to the file you want.
</p>
</div>
</div>


